# AGENT CONTEXT: This directory holds all deployable units in the monorepo.
#
# Each subdirectory here is a pnpm workspace package — an independently
# deployable app (web frontend, API server, CLI tool, etc.).
#
# NAMING CONVENTION:
#   apps/web     → @cmp/web   (primary web frontend)
#   apps/api     → @cmp/api   (backend API)
#   apps/cli     → @cmp/cli   (internal command-line tooling)
#
# STRUCTURE EXPECTATION per app:
#   apps/<name>/
#     package.json    (required — defines the workspace package)
#     src/
#     tsconfig.json   (if TypeScript)
#     README.md       (app-specific docs)
#
# DEPENDENCY RULE:
#   Apps MAY depend on packages/* (shared libraries).
#   Apps MUST NOT depend on other apps.
#   Packages MUST NOT depend on apps.
#
# CMP-10 will populate this directory with the first app template.
# This .gitkeep file can be deleted once any real content is committed here.
